reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 22, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I bought these chargers for my new phone 15 pro max. These are super long chargers and come in a pack of 2, one for my room and another for my office. These charge extremely fast! When I first received them one of the chargers wasn’t working properly, I contacted the seller and let them know about the situation. Asked if I can return only one of the chargers since the other one worked perfectly fine. They immediately mailed me another set of chargers and I received them in 2 days! So customer service is excellent as well! Overall , love these chargers, especially for the price!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 2, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Works exactly as needed
reviews.reviewText: I was pleasantly surprised with these cables. They are well-made and seem like they’ll last a long time. The length of the cable is great; I can be farther away from a plug and still charge. I would buy these again!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 5, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Durable and Sturdy
reviews.reviewText: This product works great for an aftermarket product for apple products. It charges just like an apple fast charger and has never let me down. It has been a great replacement for the original charger purchased with the iPhone.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 9, 2024
reviews.reviewText: It gets the job done, not very durable but does the job is good for the price and my daughter wanted a longer cord.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 19, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Didn’t last more than 6 weeks
reviews.reviewText: Update: the company saw my review and sent me two new cables. So 5 star customer service but the life of the new cables is TBD.Original:One of the 2 cables already stopped working. Tried different devices and charging blocks and confirmed it was the cable. I would avoid these. The return window already closed too. Yay.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 2, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great quality for the price
reviews.reviewText: These chargers beat all other chargers hand down. Other chargers stop working in a week, two if I’m lucky. I’ve made additional purchases of this item. Only replacing them because of my own accidents with breaking them. They charge super fast and I love the length of them.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 11, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Amazing length, but a bit slow.
reviews.reviewText: Length is a total win – can charge from the couch or bed without being glued to the wall. They sync up with all my Apple gear, no problem. The white color is classic Apple, but they don't juice up my devices as quick as I hoped. For a regular day, they're fine, but if you're looking for that super-speedy charge, this might not be it. Still, for the price and length, they're worth it.
